berbicara bahasa Gujarati?

00:00:52.480 --> 00:00:55.000 line:20%
Tolong, jangan berkelahi hari ini!

00:00:55.400 --> 00:00:58.360 line:20%
Bu, tolong jangan bertengkar hari ini.

